  "body": "<p>My cousins gave me this adorable Hallmark card for the baby shower and I found the perfect way to save it for Project Life.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599554613528-8N3HBK1LUE5A9XDEMCD0/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I simply used the 3x4 We R Memory Keepers punch (which was available at <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/punches/we-r-memory-keepers-3x4-punch?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a> and <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/we-r-memory-keepers-inc/143758-3x4-card-punch/\">Two Peas in a Bucket)</a> - just click Notify Me to be alerted when back in stock. The punch is easy to use, but I must admit takes a bit of muscle. I like to put it on a solid table (preferably a low table - that isn't a high countertop) and push both my palms (and arms) into it.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599554624387-L7QW3A6BF9ZA5DRGUMU8/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599554635537-UG7NEET8QUFOL1RWMPCA/14c-DSC_1212-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I saved the inside of the card with the hand written message, but love that this part can live inside of one of my Project Life pockets. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}